Product description

Color:white  |  Style:Set of 100  |  Pattern:Tealights

Solimo Tealight Candles are essentially wax candles which are packed in an aluminium case. Available in a pack of 50 & 100, these candles, are unscented and do not leave wax stains. Weighing 10g each, these compact tealight candles fit in easily into diyas or tealight holders which you can use to decorate your house for festive purposes.

From the manufacturer

Solimo Tealight Candles Enrich the ambience at your home!

Solimo Tealight Candles are essentially wax candles which are packed in an aluminium case. Available in a pack of 50 & 100, these candles, are unscented and do not leave wax stains. Weighing 10g each, these compact tealight candles fit in easily into diyas or tealight holders which you can use to decorate your house for festive purposes.

Read more



Standard burn time

With a burn time of 2-3 hours, these tealight candles are suitable for decorating the house during festive occasions and parties

Smokeless, odourless candles which do not leave soot residue

These decorative tealight candles burn without polluting the atmosphere of your home with smoke or odour. Decorate your house with these candles without worrying about any soot residue that might damage your valuable decorative items.

Burns efficiently without wax stains

These tealight candles utilise the wax and burn fully without leaving any wax stains on your furniture or the floor. Place your tealight candles on a burn-resistant surface and enjoy the refreshing ambience

Utkarsh Agrawal
TOP 500 REVIEWER
5.0 out of 5 starsLongest lasting tealight candle!!
8 November 2018
Color: whiteStyle: Set of 100Pattern: TealightsVerified Purchase
I got a bunch of these tealight candles to avoid the vagaries attached with lighting up my house during Diwali with the old fashioned candles or the diyas. After using this I would say that it will be a part of my shopping list in all the coming Diwalis.
PROS
1) You can easily light up 200 or so of these without worrying about the starting ones getting blown off or finished( I lit 200 and still the 1st one was far from being finished). In other words, these candles are unnaturally long lasting. I saw most burning to the last chip of wax.
2) It is good both for internal and external purposes. The short flame of the candle does not blow off even in a gentle breeze. The best part is that it does not leave any aftermark which makes it perfect for interiors as well.
3) The flick is long enough to easily light numerous candles at one go without grappling as is usually the case with tealights from other brands.
4) The aluminium casing makes it durable and good looking at the same time.
5) 2.7 per candle is a great bet when the normal candles which last for maximum 30 minutes come at 5-10 per piece. Most of the candles that I lit lasted for 4-5 hours. It is more than value for money.
CONS
1) The only trouble that I faced was that the double layered packing made the candles stick to each other and I spoilt some of them in the process of detaching them. A layer of paper in between could have avoided that trouble.
All in all it is a great product to light up any occasion or add a lease of life to any boring ambience.
